インストール Nginx用
$ sudo apt install certbot python3-certbot-nginx
$ sudo apt install certbot -y



新規作成時
$ sudo certbot certonly --manual -d YourDomain.com --agree-tos
または
$ sudo certbot certonly --manual -d YourDomain.com --agree-tos --register-unsafely-without-email
--メッセージ--
Saving debug log to /var/log/letsencrypt/letsencrypt.log
Plugins selected: Authenticator manual, Installer None
Obtaining a new certificate
Performing the following challenges:
http-01 challenge for YourDomain.com

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
NOTE: The IP of this machine will be publicly logged as having requested this
certificate. If you're running certbot in manual mode on a machine that is not
your server, please ensure you're okay with that.

Are you OK with your IP being logged?
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

--「Y」を入力--
(Y)es/(N)o: Y

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Create a file containing just this data:

A********************************.B********************************

And make it available on your web server at this URL:

http://wizfmsrv08.012grp.co.jp/.well-known/acme-challenge/A********************************

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Press Enter to Continue　※キーを押さずに別のウィンドウで、「A********************************」の作成作業を行う→　acme-challengeファイルの作り方
Waiting for verification...
Cleaning up challenges

--以下のメッセージがでれば成功--
IMPORTANT NOTES:
 - Congratulations! Your certificate and chain have been saved at:
   /etc/letsencrypt/live/YourDomain.com/fullchain.pem
   Your key file has been saved at:
   /etc/letsencrypt/live/YourDomain.com/privkey.pem
   Your cert will expire on 2023-07-16. To obtain a new or tweaked
   version of this certificate in the future, simply run certbot
   again. To non-interactively renew *all* of your certificates, run
   "certbot renew"
 - If you like Certbot, please consider supporting our work by:

   Donating to ISRG / Let's Encrypt:   https://letsencrypt.org/donate
   Donating to EFF:                    https://eff.org/donate-le


更新時
sudo certbot renew
sudo cp /etc/letsencrypt/live/YourDomain.com/cert.pem /opt/FileMaker/FileMaker\ Server/CStore/
sudo cp /etc/letsencrypt/live/YourDomain.com/privkey.pem /opt/FileMaker/FileMaker\ Server/CStore/
sudo fmsadmin certificate import /opt/FileMaker/FileMaker\ Server/CStore/cert.pem --keyfile /opt/FileMaker/FileMaker\ Server/CStore/privkey.pem -y -u ***** -p *****

再起動
sudo service fmshelper restart
